GQ Magazine - July 2013  USA

116 Pages | PDF | English | 21 MB 

GQ magazine is the modern man?s guide to all the things he wants to know, do, or worry about, from fashion suggestions, politics, culture, the latest gadgets on the market, sports, news, reviews, and interviews with the most intriguing celebrities around, as well as some sexy photoshoots with some of the world?s most beautiful women. It is the man?s monthly lifestyle magazine for the modern professional man with taste: his preoccupations are varied, and GQ deals with all of them.
